but we've put out a bulletin to Interpol.

225
00:16:52.500 --> 00:16:54.000
So you don't know anything.

226
00:16:55.666 --> 00:16:56.625
No.

227
00:16:58.916 --> 00:17:00.583
But I do have some photos here

228
00:17:00.666 --> 00:17:03.125
