242
00:17:39.208 --> 00:17:42.291
It was a cocktail.
often used in cases of date rape.

243
00:17:44.125 --> 00:17:47.125
No evidence of that.
the doctors didn't find any signs of it.

244
00:17:47.208 --> 00:17:49.666
